            <who name="Fabian Jakobs">fabian.jakobs</who>
            <bug_when>2007-01-08 14:26:39 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>This is not technicallly a bug in the qooxdoo code. It is a but in the qooxdoo documentation. qx.lang.Array.append is meant to append the elements of another array to the given array. Use Array.push to append objects to an array. Note that push support multiple arguments.

I have updated the API documentation in svn to clarify this.</thetext>
